ED_Title: Eradication of poverty and other development issues
ED_DecisionText: At its 49th plenary meeting, on 19  December 2023, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Second Committee.  (Footnote: A/78/464.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
